  {
    "client_msg_id": "a6f66b2f-4730-4979-a1a9-2cc6883fc752",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "One unanticipated direction I find my thoughts going is to create \"self-swallowing\" LÖVE apps where you can edit the source code right from within the app. LÖVE apps are already pretty easy to install and run; what if the editing environment was also as self-contained. Any time you run such an app you also have all the tools to modify it, right there within the app.\n\nFor a while during the week I thought, \"this is just a silly experiment, this isn't going to go anywhere because people can't use their own tools.\" But it might work if it provides a lot of convenience over the status quo.",
    "user": "UCUSW7WVD",
    "ts": "1661628588.184359",
    "team": "T5TCAFTA9",
    "blocks": [
      {
        "type": "rich_text",
        "block_id": "YvsV/",
        "elements": [
          {
            "type": "rich_text_section",
            "elements": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "One unanticipated direction I find my thoughts going is to create \"self-swallowing\" LÖVE apps where you can edit the source code right from within the app. LÖVE apps are already pretty easy to install and run; what if the editing environment was also as self-contained. Any time you run such an app you also have all the tools to modify it, right there within the app.\n\nFor a while during the week I thought, \"this is just a silly experiment, this isn't going to go anywhere because people can't use their own tools.\" But it might work if it provides a lot of convenience over the status quo."
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
